        <h1>0.5 M☉ — Red Dwarf Track</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">Fully or mostly convective, pp-chain only, with an immense main-sequence lifetime far exceeding the age of the universe — theoretically destined to end as a helium white dwarf, though none has ever had time to get there.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>pp-chain only</span><span>Fully convective</span><span>t<sub>MS</sub> ≫ t<sub>Hubble</sub></span><span>He WD (theoretical)</span></div>
