    <section class="page" id="page-m5">
      <div class="placeholder-wrap">
        <div class="ph-glyph"><svg width="60" height="60"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="24" fill="none" stroke="#7d7fa0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/></svg></div>
        <div class="ph-badge">Part I — Tracks by Mass</div>
        <h1>5 M☉ — The Classic Intermediate-Mass Track</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">The textbook Points 1–10 evolutionary sequence: convective-core main sequence, quiet helium ignition, full thermally-pulsing AGB, and a carbon-oxygen white dwarf at the end.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>Points 1–10</span><span>TP-AGB</span><span>CO WD</span></div>
        <p class="ph-note">Coming after the 1 M☉ prototype is approved.</p>
