        <p class="ph-desc">Straddles the ~8 M☉ line separating degenerate CO cores from stable carbon ignition — the fuzzy zone where the outcome could be an ONe white dwarf or an electron-capture supernova.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>M<sub>up</sub> ≈ 8 M☉</span><span>ONe WD or ECSN</span><span>Uncertain physics</span></div>
        <p class="ph-note">Coming after the 1 M☉ prototype is approved.</p>
