        <div class="ph-badge">Part I — Tracks by Mass</div>
        <h1>15 M☉ — Onion-Shell Burning</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">Builds a full onion-shell structure — H, He, C, Ne, O, Si burning layers — before core collapse triggers a Type II supernova and leaves behind a neutron star.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>Onion-shell structure</span><span>Core-collapse SN</span><span>Neutron star</span></div>
