        <h1>25 M☉ — Wolf-Rayet to Black Hole</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">Ferocious radiation-driven Wolf-Rayet winds strip the envelope down to the bare core before collapse proceeds all the way to a black hole.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>Wolf-Rayet winds</span><span>Core collapse</span><span>Black hole</span></div>
        <p class="ph-note">Coming after the 1 M☉ prototype is approved.</p>
