        <div class="ph-badge">Part II — The Six Fates</div>
        <h1>Brown Dwarf (&lt;0.08 M☉)</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">Never reaches the central temperature needed to sustain hydrogen fusion — a "failed star" that simply radiates away its gravitational energy and cools, forever.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>M &lt; 0.08 M☉</span><span>No sustained fusion</span><span>Cools indefinitely</span></div>
        <p class="ph-note">Coming after the 1 M☉ prototype is approved.</p>
