        <div class="ph-badge">Part II — The Six Fates</div>
        <h1>Red Dwarf (0.08–0.5 M☉)</h1>
        <p class="ph-desc">Fully convective, pp-chain burners with lifetimes vastly exceeding the current age of the universe — every red dwarf ever formed is, right now, still on the main sequence.</p>
        <div class="ph-meta"><span>0.08–0.5 M☉</span><span>Fully convective</span><span>Still burning today</span></div>
        <p class="ph-note">Coming after the 1 M☉ prototype is approved.</p>
